      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>diced</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>breast</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4 min or until lightly browned</p>",
      "order": 2,
